Sure, here are 20 more Midjourney Prompts with funny cats:

1. A goofy cat trying to catch its own tail, spinning around in circles and falling over in the process.
2. A curious cat exploring a new toy, using its sharp claws and playful nature to figure out how it works.
3. A sleepy cat lounging in a sunbeam, enjoying a peaceful afternoon nap.
4. A mischievous cat knocking over a vase, causing chaos and running away before getting caught.
5. A cute cat sitting on a window sill, watching the world go by with a look of wonder and awe.
6. A confident cat strutting down the street, showing off its impressive posture and attitude.
7. A brave cat standing up to a larger animal, defending its territory with courage and determination.
8. A playful cat chasing a laser pointer, leaping and pouncing with reckless abandon.
9. A sneaky cat trying to steal food from its owner's plate, using stealth and cunning to avoid getting caught.
10. A happy cat cuddling with its owner, purring and showing affection in a heartwarming moment.
11. A curious cat investigating a new scent, sniffing and exploring with its keen sense of smell.
12. A lazy cat lounging in a hammock, enjoying a lazy day in the sun.
13. A clever cat solving a puzzle, using its intelligence and wit to figure out the solution.
14. A talkative cat meowing up a storm, expressing its thoughts and feelings with a variety of sounds and tones.
15. A hungry cat begging for food, using its irresistible cuteness to get what it wants.
16. A playful cat hiding in a cardboard box, jumping out to surprise its unsuspecting owner.
17. A graceful cat leaping over obstacles, showing off its impressive agility and athleticism.
18. A mischievous cat knocking things off shelves, causing chaos and mischief wherever it goes.
19. A curious cat watching a bird outside the window, dreaming of the day when it can catch one.
20. A proud cat showing off its latest catch, whether it be a toy, a bug, or a small animal.
